file.name: negative2.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/item":
    trace:
      operationId: traceItem
      summary: Trace item
      responses:
        "200":
          description: success
        default:
          description: Success
    patch:
      operationId: updateItem
      summary: Update item
      responses:
        default:
          description: Error
          schema:
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
components:
  schemas:
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
      required:
        - code
        - message
